      <p id="space">Whether it's feedback, queries or you want your charity on Jumble, you can get in touch with us via email <span style="color:blue;text-decoration: underline;">help.Jumble@gmail.com</span>, Freephone <span style="color:blue;text-decoration: underline;">+(046) 1234567</span> or you can fill in the query forum below. If you want to put your charity on Jumble, make sure to fill in the organisation field in the forum</p></div>
      <form id="addForm" action="/Contact" method="POST">    
